thread.title: BRIEF-VBI Vaccines Announces Positive Final Phase 1 Study Results Of Preventative CMV Vaccine

title: BRIEF-VBI Vaccines Announces Positive Final Phase 1 Study Results Of Preventative CMV Vaccine
text:
May 10, 2018 / 11:33 AM / in 7 minutes BRIEF-VBI Vaccines Announces Positive Final Phase 1 Study Results Of Preventative CMV Vaccine Reuters Staff
May 10 (Reuters) - VBI Vaccines Inc:
* VBI VACCINES ANNOUNCES POSITIVE FINAL PHASE 1 STUDY RESULTS OF PREVENTATIVE CMV VACCINE
* VBI VACCINES INC - SAFE AND WELL-TOLERATED AT ALL DOSES WITH NO SAFETY SIGNALS OBSERVED IN STUDY
* VBI VACCINES INC - CMV NEUTRALIZING ANTIBODIES AGAINST FIBROBLAST CELL INFECTION INDUCED IN 100% OF SUBJECTS WHO RECEIVED HIGHEST DOSE IN STUDY Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
